item.description:
@zyle1992 wrote:

ok in your source folder, where you have your client.java, item handler and such, there should be a folder that says like character file or something like that. go into the character folder and find the text file with your name. open it up and find where it says character-items. then find an id that has a very high number on it. like 6575 or something like that. replace that with a -1. then the next number should be a 1. put a zero in it’s place and that should fix the problem.
